  "detailed_description": "<h1>THE ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/3f19d4c316e2cbfc0437788b76141941.avif?t=1771768308\" width=780 height=2386 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Casino Resort Tower</strong> is about building a casino resort skyscraper that comes alive. Run the casino floor with blackjack tables, slot machines, and poker rooms while managing everything above and below it; hotels, restaurants, staff quarters, lounges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don’t just build rooms.<br>You design a world where people live, work, wait, relax, get annoyed, recover, and move on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guests don’t pass through your tower, they experience it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And those experiences quietly shape everything that happens next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes the tower flows beautifully.<br>Sometimes it spirals into chaos.<br>And every time, it’s your design that started the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8330d276248e5618e76fe0d6e75a3a40.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8330d276248e5618e76fe0d6e75a3a40.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8330d276248e5618e76fe0d6e75a3a40.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/c30bdf3dc88a8bcde0d2eb4115b15082.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/c30bdf3dc88a8bcde0d2eb4115b15082.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/c30bdf3dc88a8bcde0d2eb4115b15082.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/0b9d1e52866f94e3cc5631183d267299.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/0b9d1e52866f94e3cc5631183d267299.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/0b9d1e52866f94e3cc5631183d267299.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Design Creates Moments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every hallway, elevator, lounge, and staff room you place changes the emotional tone of the space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy break room lifts morale.<br>A cramped corridor builds tension.<br>A long wait can turn excitement into frustration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >People react to your layout in real time, <br>moving, queuing, resting, complaining, recovering.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/ffdf7db4436468aea2b62896c7aa36d7.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/ffdf7db4436468aea2b62896c7aa36d7.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/ffdf7db4436468aea2b62896c7aa36d7.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/31d09044d808f91e73d33b0eebfde59f.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/31d09044d808f91e73d33b0eebfde59f.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/31d09044d808f91e73d33b0eebfde59f.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/dec6ddf9a13a85bfdd1abbeb1fc2da34.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/dec6ddf9a13a85bfdd1abbeb1fc2da34.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/dec6ddf9a13a85bfdd1abbeb1fc2da34.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deep, Not Punishing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casino Resort Tower is not a casual idle game,  <br>it’s a deep simulation about cause and effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it’s also forgiving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small mistakes create ripples, not dead ends. <br>Big failures become your most satisfying comebacks. <br>The tower doesn’t collapse, it adapts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re encouraged to experiment, fail, and discover how your world truly works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/3880ea1bfe484f562280fe9f64414c71.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/3880ea1bfe484f562280fe9f64414c71.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/3880ea1bfe484f562280fe9f64414c71.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/fa873798b53d43272d3147301294a4b4.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/fa873798b53d43272d3147301294a4b4.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/fa873798b53d43272d3147301294a4b4.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8e56af964a7530545563961f5c2f3a71.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8e56af964a7530545563961f5c2f3a71.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8e56af964a7530545563961f5c2f3a71.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>When Chaos Hits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elevators jam.<br>Staff get overwhelmed.<br>Guests react to the environment you created.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tower starts to push back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You step in, change the flow, add space, reroute movement, <br>and watch the mood shift in real time as the tower finds its balance again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your tower becomes a system under pressure, <br>and you’re the one rewriting its rhythm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build it.<br>Break it.<br>Bring it back stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/4e22922668d2e20c06ff53f8703650df.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/4e22922668d2e20c06ff53f8703650df.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/4e22922668d2e20c06ff53f8703650df.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casino Resort Tower is in Early Access, shaped by the people playing it, update by update. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every major update expands how your tower lives, reacts, and tells its stories.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Casino Resort Tower</strong> is about building a casino resort skyscraper that comes alive. Run the casino floor with blackjack tables, slot machines, and poker rooms while managing everything above and below it; hotels, restaurants, staff quarters, lounges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don’t just build rooms.<br>You design a world where people live, work, wait, relax, get annoyed, recover, and move on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guests don’t pass through your tower, they experience it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And those experiences quietly shape everything that happens next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes the tower flows beautifully.<br>Sometimes it spirals into chaos.<br>And every time, it’s your design that started the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8330d276248e5618e76fe0d6e75a3a40.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8330d276248e5618e76fe0d6e75a3a40.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8330d276248e5618e76fe0d6e75a3a40.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/c30bdf3dc88a8bcde0d2eb4115b15082.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/c30bdf3dc88a8bcde0d2eb4115b15082.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/c30bdf3dc88a8bcde0d2eb4115b15082.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/0b9d1e52866f94e3cc5631183d267299.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/0b9d1e52866f94e3cc5631183d267299.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/0b9d1e52866f94e3cc5631183d267299.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Design Creates Moments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every hallway, elevator, lounge, and staff room you place changes the emotional tone of the space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy break room lifts morale.<br>A cramped corridor builds tension.<br>A long wait can turn excitement into frustration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >People react to your layout in real time, <br>moving, queuing, resting, complaining, recovering.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/ffdf7db4436468aea2b62896c7aa36d7.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/ffdf7db4436468aea2b62896c7aa36d7.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/ffdf7db4436468aea2b62896c7aa36d7.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/31d09044d808f91e73d33b0eebfde59f.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/31d09044d808f91e73d33b0eebfde59f.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/31d09044d808f91e73d33b0eebfde59f.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/dec6ddf9a13a85bfdd1abbeb1fc2da34.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/dec6ddf9a13a85bfdd1abbeb1fc2da34.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/dec6ddf9a13a85bfdd1abbeb1fc2da34.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deep, Not Punishing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casino Resort Tower is not a casual idle game,  <br>it’s a deep simulation about cause and effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it’s also forgiving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small mistakes create ripples, not dead ends. <br>Big failures become your most satisfying comebacks. <br>The tower doesn’t collapse, it adapts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re encouraged to experiment, fail, and discover how your world truly works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/3880ea1bfe484f562280fe9f64414c71.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/3880ea1bfe484f562280fe9f64414c71.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/3880ea1bfe484f562280fe9f64414c71.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/fa873798b53d43272d3147301294a4b4.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/fa873798b53d43272d3147301294a4b4.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/fa873798b53d43272d3147301294a4b4.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8e56af964a7530545563961f5c2f3a71.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8e56af964a7530545563961f5c2f3a71.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/8e56af964a7530545563961f5c2f3a71.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>When Chaos Hits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elevators jam.<br>Staff get overwhelmed.<br>Guests react to the environment you created.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tower starts to push back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You step in, change the flow, add space, reroute movement, <br>and watch the mood shift in real time as the tower finds its balance again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your tower becomes a system under pressure, <br>and you’re the one rewriting its rhythm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build it.<br>Break it.<br>Bring it back stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/4e22922668d2e20c06ff53f8703650df.poster.avif?t=1771768308\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/4e22922668d2e20c06ff53f8703650df.webm?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457030/extras/4e22922668d2e20c06ff53f8703650df.mp4?t=1771768308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casino Resort Tower is in Early Access, shaped by the people playing it, update by update. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every major update expands how your tower lives, reacts, and tells its stories.</p>",
